{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":2,"day":8}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"戳穿经济主义的鬼把戏","authors":["陈家骏"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整丝弦定定音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开门见山揭画皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天不把别的表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单把那经济主义的罪行提一提。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像暴风骤雨风雷激。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级当权派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是怕来又是急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不甘心失败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗地又来耍诡计。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬的行不通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们就来软的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家金钱大把撒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想把革命左派收买去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装得一副观音脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚里尽是坏东西！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平时他们的官气大大的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候瞧他们低声又下气："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“唉！你们缺吃的？缺穿的？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这间房子有点挤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们看见公房就搬进去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对规章制度有意见？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不‘合理’的只管提，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里要是难解决，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最好是都到中央告状去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没路费，我给你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么算好咱就怎么的！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些坏东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们挑动工人要工资，要福利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煽动工人不干活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破坏国家的经济。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们要把交通来中断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬让火车开不出去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们要使工矿企业都停工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想混水来摸鱼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴谋诡计千百条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为的都是保自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派决不会自动滚下台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命同志要警惕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头可断，血可流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命意志不能移！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命造反派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大联合，大夺权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死保卫无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死保卫毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把资产阶级反动路线的新反扑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决彻底打回去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命，促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着伟大领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}